        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         There is no real spoiler to this.. it drops at the "C4" area in CT or at least that whats its called on my server..  its the Archon pyramid or area 2 on <a href="http://www.eqatlas.com/ctmap.html" target="_blank">this map</a>.  In each of the 4 corners of that area are lizards couple green and a brown..  the brown ones are placeholders for the rares(terrorclaw), you can get there without too much problem with just invis however the brown ones see though invis.  There are a few pats(roamers) in the area as well.  The left side is the easiest to take and hold because there is only one pat vise the other side (right) has 2 pats.  Anyways, it can be a long ass camp and you are gonna need a group..  this aint no solo spot <img src=icon_smile_wink.gif border=0 align=middle></P><P><font color=green>Sage Mancer</font id=green><BR><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=210518" target="_blank">My Stuff</a></P><P><BR>Edited by - Mancer Paynemaker on 06/04/2002  19:54:13<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
