        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         Correction, Terrorclaw is the named raptor that spawns as a roamer in the backside, regardless of whether you kill the brownish larger lizards in the corners. Back side is indeed the easier place to set us as you camping spot because there is only on roamer (terrorclaw or his raptor ph). Left/right got 3 roamers and front side got lots.</P><P>I know because i have spent 100s of hours in 4C camping the damn earrings.</P><P>Bring a GOOD group there. Some nameds there flurry for 300s. Braking in can get hairy if you dont time up carefully the respawn. You can straff (sp?) around corners without agroing the see invis mobs in the corners.</P><P>Fun camp, i like exp'ing there, plus loot is all droppeable so nice cash income.</P><P><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=62873" target="_blank">Yaguex</a>, warlock, <a href="http://www.mortalis.com/" target="_blank">Mortalis</a>, Antonius Bayle.<BR><a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
